#limitation(title: [ME/CFS TSPO PET Study Limitation])[
The ME/CFS TSPO PET study by Raijmakers 2021 was negative for microglial activation, contrasting with positive fibromyalgia results. The positive interpretation for ME/CFS/Long COVID relies on the hypothesis that blood-brain barrier transport confounds TSPO PET findings in these conditions, which has not been directly tested. Current evidence for neuroinflammation in ME/CFS remains extrapolated from fibromyalgia data rather than established by direct ME/CFS neuroimaging studies.
] <lim:tspo-pet-limitation>
